@680=~DISCIPLE OF THE PHOENIX: Disciples of the Phoenix see the church of Kossuth as a means of advancing towards purity. Amongst this order other clergy members of Kossuth are to be viewed as expendable, particularly those of evil alignment. Disciples of the Phoenix strongly believe that everyone should be given a chance to prove themselves as being worthy of their lords graces.

