@692=~disciple of the white rod~
@693=~Disciple of the White Rod~
@694=~DISCIPLE OF THE WHITE ROD: Loviatar teaches that the world is full of pain and torment, and the best one can do is to suffer those blows that cannot be avoided and deal as much pain back to those who offend. Disciples of the White Rod respect this view of the world and train themselves in the art of inflicting pain on others.

